            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
              Empower every person and every organization on the planet to achieve more.
            </div>
            <div class="card-footer">
              <button class="btn" id="box-features"><i class="em em-man-lifting-weights"></i> L2</button>
              <button class="btn" id="box-features"><i class="em em-money_with_wings"></i> 180 EUR</button>
